# SPA fallback for the magic-link return route ONLY.
# The assessment is a single page that reads ?token=&result= from the query
# string (new URLSearchParams(window.location.search)) and does NO path-based
# routing, so /verify is the only client-side path that must serve the app.
# A broad `/*  /index.html  200` catch-all here shadows the static Explore/
# pricing pages — e.g. /explore/sage/ would return the assessment app instead
# of the Sage archetype page. Keep this scoped to /verify and /results.
# (The root `/` serves index.html natively; real static pages serve themselves;
#  genuinely missing paths now 404, which is correct for SEO.)
# Cloudflare Pages Functions (/api/*) are matched BEFORE these static redirects.
/verify   /index.html   200
# The "My Results" magic link lands on /results?token=… — the app reads the token
# from the query string and restores the saved reading. Same SPA, scoped path.
/results  /index.html   200

# "Embodiments" was renamed to "Temperaments" (locked July 2026). Keep the old
# path working for any existing links.
/explore/embodiments/  /explore/temperaments/  301
/explore/embodiments   /explore/temperaments/  301
